        "timestamp": "2020-09-14 14:44:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nI set up terragrunt validation using \"terragrunt hclfmt --terragrunt-check\" command and this required changes posted in this commit to pass. \n\nI tried setting up validation job based on \"terragrun validate-all\" command but unfortunately it requires configured remote state backend so it's not applicable for validation.\n\nDoing hclfmt will not discover all issues in terragrunt config files (e.g. broken variable names/format) but at least allows for some basic issues discovery.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
